            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="https://pittsburgh.craigslist.org/apa/d/pittsburgh-two-bedroom-2nd-floor-quiet/7517467246.html"></div>
        </div>
Check out this two-bedroom, one bath, second floor large apartment on the Southside Flats.  The locked gated entry guides you to the charming motion sensor lighted entrance of your front door.  Up a flight of carpeted steps your private entrance takes you to a quiet living space flanked by the main well-lighted bedroom with a ceiling fan.<br>
<br>
The hallway to the bathroom and kitchen includes a convenient linen closet with lots of shelving space.<br>
<br>
The bath incorporates a full size new bathtub with shower.  The black and white checked floor lends a feel of art deco design.<br>
<br>
A newly remodeled kitchen sports all new cabinetry with a new Frigidaire dishwasher and microwave.   Click on the remote controlled ceiling fan for additional light and a cool breeze in your brightly light plank-floor spacious kitchen. <br>
<br>
Up a flight of steps and enter the very private second bedroom space.  Use this space as a bedroom, office, game room, or exercise space.  The painted floor and remote controlled ceiling fan make this room a versatile haven for your imagination.  This room also includes a large walk-in closet.<br>
<br>
Grocery store, restaurants, library, and Laundromat are all within a few blocks.  The Southside is a walking neighborhood on the bus and bicycle route.   Welcome to the quiet of the busheling Southside community.<br>
<br>
Only $1300 plus utilities. A credit check is required with application. This apartment is available September 1.  Move in requirements are security deposit, first and last months rent.  Call Cathy today for a walk though appointment  <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/pit/apa/7517467246/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
.<br>
